
         HTML::Template bundle

CHANGES

2.9_01
   - Sync up with HTML::Template 2.9 and H::T::Expr 0.07
   - Add support for subclassing H::T and H::T::E.
   - Add TMPL_ELSIF
   - Add TMPL_SET
   - Add support for <TMPL_INCLUDE <TMPL_VAR blah>>
   - Generate output to sref
   - .... and so on....

DESCRIPTION

This module combines the HTML::Template and HTML::Template::Expr
module, plus a few other goodies, into a single installable Perl.

There are too many individual enhancements to list here; look in
the doc's for more info.


DOCUMENTATION

The documentation is POD format for each of the sub-modules.  Its
also probably a good idea to read the other README's...


INSTALLATION

In case this is your first module, the usual methods are:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

CONTACT INFO

You can join the HTML::Template mailing-list.

